VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-02228', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '以  基因定序法進行16S rRNA基因序列比對之結果，若要達到菌種（species）層級之鑑定，下列何者錯誤？', '["大  於95%序列相似度，才可判定為同種（species）", "若  序列比對結果最高及第二高相似菌種序列，彼此相似度的差異性小於0.5%，則應使用其他試驗進行菌種 之確認", "以  標準參考菌株比對為最佳", "可  序列比對之基因長度，應至少500個核苷酸以上"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 67, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02229', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '具  萬古黴素抗藥性腸球菌（VRE）抗藥性基因及其表現型，下列何者最不適當？', '["帶  vanA基因的VRE對vancomycin及teicoplanin均具有高度抗藥性", "v anA基因通常位於質體上", "v anA基因可轉譯出D-ala-D-ala ligase", "v anA表現型對vancomycin的MIC約為2～4 μg/mL"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 68, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02230', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '利  用標的擴增（amplification）技術進行病毒分子檢測時，下列何組病毒與偵測標的基因的配對最適當？', '["H CV：nucleoprotein gene", "i nfluenza virus：conserved matrix gene", "S ARS-CoV-2：DNA polymerase gene", "B K virus（polyomavirus）：fusion gene"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 69, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02231', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '選  擇適合的分子檢驗方法進行細菌分型鑑定時，下列敘述何者最不適當？', '["聚  合酶連鎖反應分型法的準確性略低於脈衝式電泳分型法（pulsed field gel electrophoresis）", "配  合DNA雜交法可以增加限制酶片段長度多型性分型法（restriction fragment length polymorphism, RFLP）的辨識性與應用性", "若  無已建立之標準資料庫，不易比對不同地區之菌株資訊", "脈  衝式電泳分型法（pulsed field gel electrophoresis）可以得到欲鑑定細菌的基因序列"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 70, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02232', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下  列何者是用多對引子（primers）同時偵測多種可能病毒感染的方法？', '["n ested PCR", "m ultiplex PCR", "h ybrid capture assay", "r andom PCR"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 71, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02233', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下  列何者不是唐氏症之核型異常的成因？', '["染  色體個數異常，第21號染色體三體（trisomy 21）", "染  色體易位（translocation）", "鑲  嵌型（mosaicism）", "點  突變（point mutation）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 72, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02234', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '油  滴數位化聚合酶連鎖反應（droplet digital PCR, ddPCR）是藉由單分子油滴式隔離進行核酸拷貝數的絕 對定量；對檢測腫瘤微量突變等位比例（mutation allele frequency, MAF）有極高敏感度。圖示為利用 ddPCR收取16,000顆油滴，進行A基因野生型與突變型之螢光訊號強度的分析結果，超過閾值的油滴數目以 紅字標示。此突變等位比例為何？', '["3 .8%", "1 4.3%", "1 2.5%", "1 6.7%"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 73, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02235', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關  於基因變異（或表現異常）與肺癌發生的相關性，下列何者最正確？', '["R AS基因家族的變異常見於小細胞肺癌中", "在  肺癌細胞中，常見TP53基因與同源的p51／p73基因同時發生變異", "過  度表現的MYC基因家族常見於小細胞肺癌與非小細胞肺癌", "H ER2基因大量表現是肺癌病人具有較佳預後的指標"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 74, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02236', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', 'E RCC1（excision repair cross complementing 1）基因的單一核苷酸多型性會影響oxaliplatin治療腸胃 道相關惡性腫瘤的效果，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["C 變異成G是 ERCC1基因最常見的單一核苷酸多型性", "單  股核酸結構多樣性法不適用於檢測ERCC1基因的單一核苷酸多型性", "C C同合子基因型對oxaliplatin治療的反應最差", "T T同合子基因型對oxaliplatin治療的反應為中等"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 75, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02237', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '血  癌病人在經過治療之後，多數病人血液或骨髓中的癌細胞分別降至1／100或1／1000以下，下列何種方法 最有可能偵測到這些微量殘存的癌細胞？', '["原  位螢光雜交分析", "南  方墨點分析", "染  色體核型分析", "即  時定量聚合酶連鎖反應"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c376b2134086", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ae5d9680e26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 76, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
